  "prompt": "Which is the best laptop for around 40k?",
  "response": "As of my last update, here are some good laptop options available around the \u20b940,000 price range in India. Please note that prices and availability can vary based on location and any sales or discounts:\n\n1. **HP 15s**:\n   - Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3\n   - 8GB RAM (expandable)\n   - 512GB SSD\n   - 15.6-inch FHD display\n   - Lightweight and good battery life\n\n2. **Acer Aspire 5**:\n   - Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3\n   - 8GB RAM (expandable)\n   - 512GB SSD\n   - 15.6-inch FHD display\n   - Good build quality and performance\n\n3. **Lenovo IdeaPad Slim 3**:\n   - Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3\n   - 8GB RAM (expandable)\n   - 512GB SSD\n   - 15.6-inch FHD display\n   - Solid performance for everyday tasks\n\n4. **ASUS VivoBook 14**:\n   - Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3\n   - 8GB RAM (with options to upgrade)\n   - 512GB SSD\n   - 14-inch FHD display\n   - Sleek design and portability\n\n5. **Dell Inspiron 15**:\n   - Intel Core i3 / AMD Ryzen 3\n   - 8GB RAM (expandable)\n   - 512GB SSD\n   - 15.6-inch FHD display\n   - Reliable build quality and decent battery life\n\nWhen choosing a laptop, consider what you'll primarily use it for (like work, gaming, or graphic design) and select specifications accordingly. Always check the latest reviews and user feedback for the specific model you are interested in, as availability and prices can change.",
